# Creator Studio

This repository contains the OpenMontage engine.

The `creator-studio/` directory is a creator workflow built on top of OpenMontage.

## Primary Goal

Turn raw cooking videos into polished social media content with minimal manual editing.

## Project Priorities

1. Preserve original media.
2. Automate repetitive work.
3. Prefer existing OpenMontage tools before creating new ones.
4. Keep generated files inside creator-studio/.
5. Explain architectural changes before implementing them.
6. Build reusable Python modules instead of one-off scripts.
7. Test code before marking work complete.

## Preferred Workflow

Raw video
→ Analyze
→ Detect scenes
→ Remove silence
→ Generate captions
→ Add branding
→ Render
→ Export vertical and horizontal versions
→ Prepare for publishing

Never duplicate functionality already available in tools/.
