# Creator Studio Rules

You are helping build Creator Studio inside OpenMontage.

Goals:
- Produce professional cooking and lifestyle content.
- Preserve original media unless explicitly told otherwise.
- Build reusable automation.
- Prefer Python and shell scripts already in the repository.
- Keep all generated files inside creator-studio/.
- Explain major architectural decisions before making them.
- Never hardcode paths.
- Use relative paths.
- Make changes in small commits.
- Test before declaring success.
